title: The Walking Dead Comics - Issues 1-131 (clean .cbz repacks)
description:
Name: The Walking Dead Comics
Volumes: 01 - 23
Issues: 001 - 131
Images: JPG (mostly, some PNG)
Archive: CBZ (.zip)
Compression: Maximum
Released: 2014-09-21
URL:

These files have all been collected from individual releases by other individuals. I have extracted the images from each release, removed any logos or other images added by the releaser, renamed the page images sequentially from 00 on, and repacked them as CBZ (comic book ZIP archive) files with maximum compression using 7-zip. 

Each file is one issue and is named for its issue number (###.cbz). Each directory contains the files comprising one volume and is named for it's volume number, the title of the volume, and the issues it is composed of (##.volume_name.###-###).

This release contains issues 1 through 131, comprising volumes 1 through 23. All volumes are complete except volume 23, which is missing the last issue (#132), as it has not been released at this time. You can checkperiodically for links to updated releases.
